ProductionRateMultiplierDescription: Adjusts the production rate. Higher values make industries produce goods faster, but may also increase traffic congestion. This setting affects all industries (Mod default).
SureToResetCustomizedIndustriesSettings: Will reset all customized industries settings to default. This action cannot be undone. Are you sure you want to continue?
LoadGame: In order to ensure the normal operation of Rebalanced Industries Revisited Mod, load game function has been disabled, please exit the game and reload save.
LoadMultiplierFactor: トラック積載量の倍率
LoadMultiplierFactorMinor: オプションを調整するとトラックの最大積載量が変化して、数値を上げるとトラックはより多くの荷物を積載して輸送できます。 同時に抽出施設と加工施設の生産力も大きくなり、より多くのトラックで輸送を可能にします。
ModDescription: Rebalances Industries DLC, reduce traffic flow, increase cargo loading and more.
OpenControlPanel: コントロールパネルを開く
OtherFunctionsMinor: コントロールパネルの呼び出しは、ショートカットキー・UUIボタンを使用します。 コントロールパネルでオプションを調整したい場合は、事前にオプションパネルを閉じて下さい。
ToMainMenu: In order to ensure the normal operation of Rebalanced Industries Revisited Mod, back to main menu function has been disabled, please exit the game and reload save.
Changelog_v1_0_0_Attention: This update automatically resets all settings.
Changelog_v1_0_0_Added: Added unique factory output rate adjustment options.
Changelog_v1_0_0_Added1: Added custom properties for industrial buildings, including construction cost, maintenance cost, truck count, output rate, work place, and storage capacity.
Changelog_v1_0_0_Added2: Added mod default values, game default values, custom options to modify industrial building properties.
Changelog_v1_0_1_Added: Added global production rate adjustment for extractors, processors, and unique factories (Mod Default).
Changelog_v1_0_1_Added1: Added compatibility support for the Campus Industries Housing Mod.
Changelog_v1_0_1_Added2: Added support for the Fishing Harbor building.
Changelog_v1_0_1_Fixed: Fixed an issue where the entry button was still displayed on certain unavailable industrial buildings.
Changelog_v1_0_1_Fixed1: Fixed a potential deserialization issue that could prevent the mod from working.
Changelog_v1_0_2_Added: Added more custom settings for fishing buildings.
Changelog_v1_0_2_Fixed: Fixed an issue where the configuration was incorrect when selecting different configuration types.
